												<p>Tyler Malone is a writer based in Southern California. He is the founder and Editor-in-Chief of <i>The Scofield</i> as well as a Contributing Editor at <i>Literary Hub</i>. His writing has appeared in the <i>Los Angeles Times, Laphamâ€™s Quarterly, the LA Review of Books</i>, and elsewhere.</p>
